Sino-Tibetan. Compare {{cog|my|လို||to want; to desire}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Alternatively, from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*r-ju(w)||to ask; to request}}, whence {{cog|bo|ཞུ||to request}} ([[ibid.]]).

